				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${F}_{nadir}$$\end{document}, the power system can accept more RESs instead of CSGs, otherwise the limit of RESs can be calculated from the previous loop.Fig. 5
Algorithm of determining the acceptable level of RESs for achieving frequency stability

